OL,4,G2215FBeach Boys: Good Vibrations Tour
OL,5,     GThis biographical musical film
OL,6,     Gdirected by Gary Weis intertwines
OL,7,     G1976 concert footage with
OL,8,     Ginterviews with the band, along
OL,9,     Gwith Blues Brothers Dan Aykroyd
OL,10,     Gand John Belushi.
OL,11,G2315FThe Beach Boys: Endless Harmony
OL,12,     GWith contributions from members
OL,13,     Gof the band, hear the definitive
OL,14,     Gstory of the Beach Boys - one of
OL,15,     Gthe most successful bands ever
OL,16,     Gwho went toe to toe with the
OL,17,     GBeatles.
